0.02 2023-06-06T01:40:21Z

    - Comply with MB's clean action
    - Return list of libs (currently disorganized)
    - Attempt to die when SDL3 fails to build

0.01 2023-06-05T17:54:25Z

    - original version
    - installs whatever is at the tip of main
